{"action": "edit", "code": "def replace_regions(input_array):\n    output = np.copy(input_array)\n    rows, cols = output.shape\n    for i in range(rows):\n        for j in range(cols):\n            if output[i][j] == 0:\n                for m in range(rows - i):\n                    for n in range(cols - j):\n                        if output[1:i + m + 1, j:j + n + 1].sum() > 0:\n                            break\n                    if output[1:i + m + 1, j:j + n + 1].sum() > 0:\n                        break\n            if m > 1 and n > 1:\n                output[1:i + m, j:j + n] = 2\n    return output\ndef main(input_array):\n    output = replace_regions(input_array)\n    return output", "user_code": "def replace_regions(input_array):\n    output = np.copy(input_array)\n    (rows, cols) = output.shape\n    for i in range(rows):\n        for j in range(cols):\n            if output[i][j] == 0:\n                for m in range(rows-i):\n                    for n in range(cols-j):\n                        if output[1:i+m+1,j:j+n+1].sum()>0:\n                            break\n                    if output[1:i+m+1,j:j+n+1].sum()>0:\n                        break\n            if m>1 and n>1:\n                output[1:i+m,j:j+n] = 2\n    return output\n\ndef main(input_array):\n    output = `replace the regions bigger than 1*1 All-zero zone with 2 `(input_array)\n    return output\n", "gpt_code": "", "holes": {}}
